OL,5, About four million UK households will  
OL,6, face higher mortgage payments next     
OL,7, year, the Bank of England has said,    
OL,8, with the typical payment up by #250.   
OL,10,FThe average monthly mortgage bill would
OL,11,Fgo up from #750 to #1,000, the Bank's  
OL,12,FFinancial Stability Report said.       
OL,14,FThe rising cost would cause severe     
OL,15,Ffinancial difficulties for another     
OL,16,F220,000 households, the Bank said.     
OL,18,FBusinesses would also be under         
OL,19,F"significant pressure" owing to rising 
OL,20,Fprices and borrowing costs, it added.  
